Class Customers

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Customers
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Buyers, Sellers
    public abstract class Customers
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is a value object for Customers and contains an observable list of customers to hold and manage POJO reference types.
